Altus Strategies has announced that it has signed a definitive Purchase & Sales agreement and Net Smelter Return royalty agreements with Stellar Africa Gold in respect of Altus’ Prikro and Zenoula gold projects in Côte d’Ivoire. Steven Poulton, CE of Altus, comments: “We are pleased to conclude this royalty and equity transaction with Stellar on our two prospective gold projects in Ivory Coast. “Altus is focused on realising value from a high quality, diversified and precious metal focused portfolio of royalty assets. “This transaction further underscores our royalty generation strategy and we look forward to Stellar’s exploration progress on the Projects”. Highlights:  